Netflix Analysis: 14 Business Problems

 1. Count the total number of Movies versus TV Shows currently available on Netflix.
 2. Identify and list all movies that were released in the year 2020.
 3. Determine the top 5 countries with the highest amount of content (Movies & TV Shows) on the platform.
 4. Find the movie with the longest duration (runtime) in the entire dataset.
 5. List all TV Shows that were specifically produced in India.
 6. Retrieve all content (Movies and TV Shows) directed by 'Kirsten Johnson'.
 7. List all movies that are categorized under the 'Documentaries' genre.
 8. Find the total number of content items associated with each rating (e.g., PG-13, TV-MA, etc.).
 9. Identify and list all shows that were added to the Netflix library during the month of September.
 10. Identify directors who have directed a minimum of 10 movies or TV shows on the platform.
 11. Classify content into two categories: 'Old' (released before 2010) and 'New' (released in 2010 or later).
 12. Determine the specific year in which Netflix added the highest volume of content to its platform.
 13. Calculate the average release year for each content type (Movie vs. TV Show).
 14. Identify the top 10 actors who have appeared in the highest number of movies or TV shows produced in India.
